******Assignment 2 : Radviz Implementation******
******Meghna R Holla B00812604******

Code to implement the basic functionality of Radviz Chart using D3.js library.

Features added:
1. Default Radviz Chart on page load 
2. File Upload option to select a different CSV file (csv file to be selected from the project's local 'data' directory on downloading the project)
3. Check boxes to make Anchor selection. The chart re-renders based on checked/unchecked checkboxes.
3. Slider to change the opacity of the data points
4. Anchors can be moved around on the circumference of the circle. 
5. Legend is displayed. On hovering over the values on the legend, respective points will get highlighted
6. On hovering over each data point, details wrt to that point is shown on tooltip
7. On hovering over each anchor, tooltip to determine the position of anchors is given.
8. On selecting a different file using the upload button, one can go back to the default chart by clicking 'Default Radviz'
9. On moving the anchors on the circle, one can go back to the default anchor positions by clicking 'Reset Anchor Position'
10. The data used are normalized

